description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Daily Breathing Exercises in 12 Minutes | Better Health & Wellness | Saurabh Bothra' from the channel Saurabh Bothra.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join Free Yoga Challenge -  https://habuild.yoga/free
Join our WhatsApp Community: https://habuild.yoga/community

Check out my last video on 7-Minute Daily Workout to Control Blood Circulation  - https://youtu.be/JcZo9OSCS_Q
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Have you ever stopped to think about how you breathe? Most of us go through our day without even noticing our breath, but did you know that daily breathing exercises can have a huge impact on your overall well-being? Today, I’m going to show you how something as simple as breath control can lead to significant changes in your body and mind. In this video, we’ll explore how incorporating daily breathing exercises into your routine can help reduce stress, improve focus, and even boost your lung capacity.
